En fin... Bienvenido chico nuevo, a partir de ahora seré tu venerado jefe de esta maravillosa tienda.
Tu deber es cobrar debidamente a los clientes que aquí vienen ¿Sencillo verdad?
Como no quiero saturar tu cerebro diminuto el primer día, solo veremos dos direcciones: arriba y derecha.
A la derecha verás una caja registradora donde te aparecerá el dinero que ha traído el cliente.
Más a la derecha tendrás una tabla con los precios estándar de los productos que aquí se venden.
Si miras arriba verás dos cadenas cada una con un uso concreto. ¡ATIENDE!
Si es una cuerda con moho verde, es la que tirarás de ella cuando el cliente traiga todo correcto.
Si es una cadena con agarre roja, es la que tirarás cuando algo no te cuadre en las cuentas.
¿Cobras bien? Monedita para tú ¿Cobras mal? Olvídate de tus propinas.
Las propinas las tienes en el bote de la izquierda, pero prefiero no indicarte otra dirección más hoy.
No creo que mi seguro cubra lo que sea que le pase a tu cerebro si se sobrecarga.
Suerte chico nuevo, la vas a necesitar.
Greetings, citizen. The one and only Geeraard has arrived. You’re welcome, you’re welcome...
Why aren’t you crying with joy yet? Why aren't you begging for my autograph while on your knees?
You don’t know who I am?! Everyone here does. I’m the hero of heroes, who defeated the Demon King with a dagger and a blindfold.
Come on… all my fans (basically the entire kingdom) know I’m the greatest hero in history!
Just charge me for this, maybe it’ll make this less… uncomfortable.
Human, you should read some of my epic tales! I’ll maybe even autograph it next time.
OUTRAGEOUS! At least learn how to count coins, fool!
Hic… Heeeyy… you’re not the usssual guy… hic.

Just cause I’m 22 hic… I’m in the prime of my youth!
Anyway… hic, charge me already.
Thanks buddy hic, you’re my new favorite human..!
Meh... the other guy was better hic.
Hey… uh… I’m Anthony.
I’m so tired I’m not even alive anymore… haha… literally.
Sorry for the bad jokes… just ring me up.
Thanks… Wait- Why do I have two extra coins..?
Oh, I was missing two coins, my bad..!
Greetings from my bleak existence…
To be a tapestry is to live a decorative slavery.
My life is like an emo song: long, sad… and poorly stitched.
Charge me before this day depresses me even more.
Thanks… one less sorrow today.
Another shadow woven into my tapestry.
Oh poor me… Once a samurai,  now a noodle heater…
UWAA! Forgive me, young one. Good morning!
I’m in a bit of a rush, if you don’t mind, young human.
Have a nice day, young human!
Oh no! A single coin short..! I hope I don’t get fired..!
Hello dear, this place seriously needs an elevator.
It’s exhausting not having my husband around…
I ate him, and raising my little one alone is harder now.
That reminds me I need to go to the zoo and fetch him. Could you charge me, please?
Thanks. I hope your partner eats you soon too.
Now my son won’t have a pet. Thanks.
Ahoy! I’m Giovanni, and I found a new cookbook called: Neck…Ronomicon..! Or something like that…"
I’m about to cook something divine, literally (it says it on page 137)."
These are the ingredients for my dish!
Grazzie! You’ll maybe get to taste it sometime.
Mamma miva! Without this… no recipe!
H-hi… s-sorry for the st-stuttering…
I w-want to buy this for my d-dad…
It’s a d-dead cat… but with love… please charge me.
Th-th-thank you… he’ll l-love it.
D-d-darn… I w-wanted to surprise him…
I bet you’re exhausted… well I don’t care.
A little birdie — called the Employment Inspector — told me you’re homeless.
Lucky you’ve got a generous and filthy rich boss like me… I’ll lend you one of the best homes in the kingdom.
That wonderful place is… my mom’s basement.
Hope you like it!
Morning, newbie.
How was your first day? I thought that- Eh, I’ll be honest, I don’t care.

Wizards get discounts, and the rest of the races… work extra hours!
Also, several drinks are now banned for some races.
Check the rules — they’re on the left side of your screen.
Good luck, newbie.
Hey, human.
That walking microwave from yesterday? Gave you the wrong amount of coins.
I brought one extra coin so they can fire him.
Anyway, charge me for this.
Later, dumb human.
Can’t even count? You just lost the real type of clients.

Thanks! You’ll maybe get to taste it~!

Hey tiny one! I’m Manny Pointy Top.

Good morning? I dunno… I only see purple.
You might be confused: eyes up here — I’m the orb that talks.

I saw a guy with a weird book doing some ritual, and when he saw me — whack! Orb to the face.
Then I woke up, like this. Guess it’s not too bad, since I still have my… date~.
Life’s short, and that mangaroo is totally my type.
I need to look good… well, as good as an orb can.
Anyway, hope they catch the guy soon before the detective bugs me.
Go ahead and charge me for these potions — I’ve got a date in a few minutes!
Thanks, bro! Wish me luck!
Dude! I had all the money..?!
Hey there! Today’s my first day as an explorer.
I replaced a drunk hippo-toad… crazy story, really!

Wish me luck on my first day!
Oh no… this stuff was for work…
Hey buddy! How ya doing? Great? Awful?
I’M TERRY-FIC! HAHAHA!!!

Birthdays, weddings, bachelor parties, and… FUNERALS!

I became a race car, but I’m still a dishwasher.

Good pet!!!

¿Eres nuevo por aquí? Me llamo…
¡Espera, que llegaré tarde!

The victim kept going on about a date, but I think they’ll be waiting a while now.

Have you seen any of your customers carrying something like that?

Check the rules — left side of your screen.
Good luck, newbie.

Heeeyyy hic… I’m here for my be-beers hic.
Man, I remember the days when I was young, sober, and had a future… hic.

But I said no. I have principles… even if they’re a bit blurry.
Charge me before I pass out on the counter.

N-no worries hic… the other guy was worse…

Need talk better with runes so me no sound crazy.

Hey cashier! I’m finally a REAL explorer!

Full of rusty traps, broken holograms, and a haunted toaster!
We only found dust, an old slime, and a grandma talking about her ex…
Still awesome. Think I found my calling!
Need this rune for tomorrow’s dimensional rift trip! So excited!
Thanks! I’m giving it my all!
Really? I just started and already I’m fired?!
Hey kid… this is still a store, right?
You remind me of my grandson… before he exploded.
These items bring back memories…
This rune reminds me of my brother… and the beer reminds me of my ex-husband…
Actually, everything reminds me of my ex… anyway, charge me.
Thanks sweetie. You’re just as kind as that doctor who scraped the rust off my soul.
Ah… this feels like my second crisis after divorcing that waffle iron.
You survived another day… that’s starting to feel like a miracle.
Go rest in my mother’s basement.
Good night, human.
Morning, human.
Today starts a new promo: “Bring your filthy coupon”.
People can now bring in Coupons — a new race used as currency.
If they have one, they get the coupon promo item for free.
Now get to work!
Yo, bro! I survived the date… I think.
Now I need emotional and magical energy.
I wanna give her a potion — she’s the woman of my dreams.
Hope the new coupon deal works.
Should get me one item for free!
Thanks, bro! Really appreciate it!
Hey! Don’t you know how to check coupons or what?!
Yo, my dude.
Need some stuff for my latest mixes, y’know?
This should do the trick… or my boss is gonna kill me.
Nice, bro! You’re top-tier!
Great… I just lost my job. Thanks, human.
Hey hey!
Found this coupon in a cave yesterday.
Hope it works for today’s shopping!
Please charge me right — I need this for my mission!
Thanks! Now I’ve got the energy to keep exploring!
Oh no… that was important… Hope I make it anyway.
Hellooo there…
I’m recovering from a little incident.
Someone sold an energy drink to my limbastic.
My summoned creature! Took forever to convince the church to do the ritual…
Ingredients were insanely expensive. Had to order some through astral express shipping.
Anyway…
I need some drinks — with caffeine, please.
I might read your chronicles someday… if you’re worthy.
HOW DARE YOU!
Yo yo! I’m Patxi — the bag runner.
Literally run with bags.
Total opposite of my boyfriend Anthony.
He’s a bit slower — needs these drinks to survive coding.
Like any programmer — no caffeine, no API calls.
You know, right?
Anyway, charge me — this is for my sweetheart.
Efficiency! My babe’s gonna be back from the dead in no time!
Ugh… my boyfriend’s not gonna be happy about missing his caffeine…
I need you, filthy human! I lost my slime — Carlos II!
Espero que no se haya fugado con ese gnomo que anda suelto por la tienda.
Help me find him in this box…
Do it before I explode you!
It worked! I owe you… maybe I’ll give you a slime minion.
Useless human. Carlos II will hate you forever.
Hey handsome! I’m Magmachine, the hottest washer in the kingdom.
I’ve got a “Shake Booties at the Club” setting tonight.
But first… I need this magical combo.
With this charm and my wallet, I’ll pay you.
Mmm… fast hands! I like that.
Oof… cold much? You resisted all my charms.
Ahh! The store finally receives me!
I’m Bonnie, the Bone Elemental — tragic star of the NecroArt Museum.
I used to walk dinosaur catwalks… now I’m a coat rack.
But today, darling, I treat myself.
A beer for my sorrows… a dead cat to end my loneliness.
Charge me well, sweetie, or I’ll collapse dramatically right here.
Divine! You’ve treated me like the legend I am!
How horrid! And I came ready to spend my star salary!
Morning sugar. You’re such a good worker, I can tell."
Should’ve followed your example instead of going on that awful date…
Gave love another shot… spent hours on my Hybrinder profile…
Met at Bareau's small nightclub, claws freshly sharpened…"
And turns out — not even a hybrid.
Dude had a giant orb for a head.
Still went to dinner, but blocked him right after."
My lucky claw must’ve stopped working — it’s from my ex-husband.
Sorry if I bored you… charge me, sweetie. I’ve got more stores to hit.
Thanks honey… hope your dates go better than mine.
This stuff’s banned? Weird… saw other people buy it yesterday.
Yo, fellow wage slave.
Slept 40 minutes… not even in a row.
My partner made me go running at sunrise.
Said it was romantic — squats at dawn with weights.
I’m more tired than debugging cursed code.
Let’s see if this ramen gets me through the day…
Thanks… hope I don’t fall asleep programming a golem’s respiratory system.
Welp… another bug in real life. I’m used to it.
Yooo!
Worked a bachelor party with Rave-n yesterday…
She was on the DJ deck — I was on the dance floor.
There were lights, fog, streamers… and a crystal ball that, well…
Let’s say I now appreciate padded chairs a bit more.
Ended up in a very… uncomfortable situation.
But hey, we laughed! And used ointment.
Anyway, charge me! Got another party tonight!
Now THAT’s what I’m talking about! Thanks, bro!
Coupon doesn’t work? Oh well… at least it doesn’t hurt as much as sitting today.
Good morning, clerk. Looks like you've had a busy shift.
Yesterday we sent Detective León to question the suspects. Turns out Giovanni *did* know something.
He was in possession of an ancient spellbook — banned centuries ago, though no one remembers why.
He was also seen near the gas station where the victim worked the same night.
But after checking, we confirmed his story. He’s off the suspect list.
However, we found something else — someone from this shop may be involved.
A receipt from the scene shows someone bought a crystal ball under the name “Manolo.”
Do any of the following match that description?
Thanks again. We’re getting closer. Have a good day, human.
Morning, not-so-newbie.
You’ve got the coupon thing down, even with that tiny brain of yours.
Today brings a new kind of coupon — and every day after will too.
Don’t even think about scamming my customers! I want their gold!
Oh, by the way… what did you do to my ice mage?
I know it was you...
But hey, I guess he needed a vacation after working without a contract.
Anyway — WORK HARD, HUMAN!
Hey there, human… can you help me?
I’ve decided to ditch the weird mage who summoned me.
Who even resurrects someone without permission?!
Anyway, I need two energy drinks to go 100% and escape the kingdom.
Internet said this stuff gives super speed.
Soooo… will you help me?
Knew you’d help. Take my sword as thanks. You’ve earned it.
Really? No heart at all...
Hey, stupid human.
You’re still not fired? Shame.
Can’t believe someone like you is still working here.
Charge me, loser.
First thing you’ve done right, idiot.
Damn rules…
Oh sweetie… it’s so hot today…
Back in my day, we fixed that with a hose and a good ol’ water jug.
Now we’ve got cold beer. How modern of me!
Go on, darling — ring me up before I change my mind… I might’ve already.
You’re such a sweetheart… like my grandson. Or maybe it was my toaster.
It’s okay, honey. You were probably distracted.
At last! My limbastic and I are off on a mission.
All thanks to that strange church.
Time to gear up properly.
Luckily, I chose this shop to get my essentials.
Charge me, humble fan!
We shall meet again. Take this signed photo of me, in case you forget my greatness.
HOW DARE YOU!
MY LIMBASTIC ESCAPED BECAUSE OF YOU!
I saw the receipt — YOU sold him energy drinks!
I’m going to report your stupid store to the inspector!
It took so much effort to bring him back with help from the church!
BUDDY, I NEED YOU — BADLY!
BEER’S BANNED FOR HYBRIDS NOW!
I STARTED TALKING PROPERLY AGAIN!
I EVEN GOT A JOB OFFER!
I DON’T WANNA WORK AGAIN!
Especially not with that PETRA girl who stole my old gig!
NO WAY!
